==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# one who regards or judges with partiality. one who respects.
#:''For these two were old friends, old mates both at school and college, both thorough respecters of themselves and each other..'' (Robert Louis Stevenson)
# a person who respects someone or something; usually used in the negative; "X is no respecter of Y".

